e34d70d1-fa96-443b-b58b-8c27f217cd09.title: Quest for Code: Text Adventure Game
e34d70d1-fa96-443b-b58b-8c27f217cd09.description: Design and code an interactive text-based adventure game from scratch. This project will teach core programming concepts like variables, control flow, functions, and user input handling through hands-on development. You will build game logic, manage states, and implement user choices to create a compelling, playable story.

3c3b31c5-9a07-4546-badc-7adb16fe7fa5.title: Quest for Code: Text Adventure Game
3c3b31c5-9a07-4546-badc-7adb16fe7fa5.description: Design and code an interactive text-based adventure game from scratch. This project will teach core programming concepts like variables, control flow, functions, and user input handling through hands-on development. You will build game logic, manage states, and implement user choices to create a compelling, playable story.
deliverables: Functional Game Core: Implement room navigation, command parsing, and the main game loop.
Inventory & Interaction System: Code for managing player inventory, items, and object interaction logic.
Branching Storyline Logic: Develop conditional pathways, puzzles, and at least two distinct endings based on player choices.
Robust User Input & Error Handling: Implement clear input processing, validation, and graceful error management for invalid commands.
Well-documented & Modular Codebase: Deliver clean, commented code structured into logical functions or modules.
